import React from "react";
import {NavLink} from 'react-router-dom'




const Header = ()=>{
    return(<>
   <header> <navbar>
        <NavLink activeClassName="active-class" to="./">Home</NavLink>
        <NavLink activeClassName="active-class" to="./contact">Contacts</NavLink>
        <NavLink activeClassName="active-class" to="./about">About</NavLink>
        <NavLink activeClassName="active-class" to="./services">Services</NavLink>
    </navbar>
    </header>
     
    </>)
}


export default Header;
